            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It was my exam centre. It's at very accessible location. I don't know if it's a college or a 10+2 school. The campus is huge. And somewhat maintained. A couple of issue I got was with staff. It's seemed they are conducting exam for the first time. No idea where to store bags or phones. I don't know if they are regular staff or not and most seemed off least interested in conducting exam. Another thing is that's in most test centre's(not in iON but mostly in OMR ones) they do offer water in between sessions but there wasn't a single time anyone was offered drinking water.",
