            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This college is located in Noida sector 91 and it's not difficult to go here with any convenience. Nearest metro station is the sector 137 of the Noida Metro Rail Corporation (NMRC).\nThe college is not for graduation or post graduation courses, it's for matriculation and intermediate studies in various streams. It's well maintained by the authorities and it has been spread in a wide area. The infrastructure facilities, education facilities, park, etc. is beautifully organised and maintained here.\nI've recently visited this college due to my CA (Chartered Accountancy) exams for the June 2023 sessions. The college authority had provided proper arrangements for the students to keep their mobile phones and bags; also they have provided proper waiting and sitting arrangements for the parents waiting for their children who were giving exams; however, when half an hour was left for exams, they advised parents to wait outside for their children.",
          "publisher": {
